        <h3 id="summary">Summary</h3>

        <p>
            In this article we learn't how to check for equality in data between collections using <Highlight>SequenceEqual</Highlight>. This can be used to 
            find if item is between collection matches or not and also we can compare object item using Comparer. All these can be used with any <Highlight>IEnumerable</Highlight> or 
            <Highlight>IQueryable</Highlight> types.
        </p>
